:: Loop Test
Test \@while:
@($i = 0)
<ul>@while($i <= 10) {
  <li>List Item Number $i</li>
  @($i++)
}</ul>
\
Test \@for:
@($a = ["apple", "orange", "banana"])
<ol>@for($food of $a) {
  <li>$food</li>
}</ol>
\
Test \@break:<br>
Expected: 1 2 3 4 5<br>
Actual:
@(_i = 0)
@while(true) {
  @(_i++)
  _i
  @if(_i >= 5) {
    @break()
  }
}

Test \@continue:<br>
Expected: 1 2 20 3 4 40 5 6 60 7 8 80 9 10 100<br>
Actual:
@(_i = 0)
@while(_i < 10) {
  @(_i++, _j = _i * 10)
  _i
  @if(_i % 2) { @continue() }
  _j
}

